whydpi (1.0.1-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Public release on a fresh repository.  Adaptive, per-SNI TLS
    fragmentation with parallel strategy discovery; DoH stub resolver;
    IPv4/IPv6 transparent proxy; CDN IP-range rotation via multi-resolver
    DoH and prefix-aware alternate selection; Encrypted-ClientHello
    neutralisation at the DNS stub; multi-record ClientHello reassembly;
    cached-passthrough fall-through to discovery; cross-platform system
    tray; Windows WinDivert decoy fragmentation fallback; commit hooks and
    Cursor rules blocking Co-authored-by trailers.

